hortintroductions.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.veryshortintroductions.com%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=4a8e8509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.veryshortintroductions.com/</a><br />\n請個相關學科專家黎，以咩都未學過既人做對像去寫，深入淺出簡介一個思想/思想家/一個學科，一本大約110頁左右。<br />\n呢個系列既書陸陸續續都有譯緊做中文 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oupchina.com.hk/en/general-interest/humanities/vsi#kierkegaard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oupchina.com.hk%2Fen%2Fgeneral-interest%2Fhumanities%2Fvsi%23kierkegaard&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=3b2359f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.oupchina.com.hk/en/general-interest/humanities/vsi#kierkegaard</a><br />\n<br />\n推廣香港人讀書風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拋磚引玉歡迎傾下。"},{"pid":"de72699e23d2c0355d8852215f7ed694c8a61bb0","tid":1792544,"uid":258570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T18:56:05.000Z","msg":"留名追Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新手BB班，成日都去誠品打書釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646e6897d2de5bfb56d66fd37ac1b49fd4529133","tid":1792544,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4520cf5a4ff43cf6b1ca6c34bfdceec39d3d3286","tid":1792544,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"上面有人推薦咗啲原典，但新手未必須要急住啃原典。<br />\n讀完原典啲字面意思，同理解到原典所呈現既想法同源流係兩個境界。打好底再去讀會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n中文書都有好多好既啟蒙書同作者，下面有啲人名，無頭緒既話追黎睇 : <br />\n政治/道德哲學 : <br />\n周保松 政治的道德 / 自由人的平等政治 <br />\nMichael Sandel (桑德爾) 正義/金錢買不到的東西<br />\n中國哲學 : <br />\n唐君毅 人生之體驗 / 人生隨筆 <br />\n香港政治 : <br />\n羅永生 殖民家國外<br />\n鄺健銘 雙城對倒<br />\n顧汝德 官商同謀 / 失治之城<br />\n<br />\n英文唔拘的話，英文就真係好多好既文史哲思考啟蒙書 (人地英語地區搞得起相關既巿場) <br />\n推薦一個系列 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.veryshortintroductions.com/\" data-sr-url=\"htt